# Dogfood diagnostic capture (dispatch 000039)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The diagnostics capture log holds REAL source snippets from the .ps1 files you
# edit while dogfooding the plugin. It is LOCAL-ONLY and must NEVER be committed.
# The whole dogfood/ directory is ignored so no captured snippet can ever be
# staged -- do not weaken this. See README -> "Dogfood diagnostic capture".
/dogfood/

# Pinned-PSSA .nupkg cache (dispatch 000049)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# A local restore/save dir for the pinned, hash-verified PSScriptAnalyzer .nupkg,
# used only when POWERSHELL_LSP_PSSA_CACHE points here (CI sets it under the
# workspace). It is a build artifact, never source -- never commit it.
/.pssa-nupkg-cache/
